{"tid":1479914,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬鞍山Pepe 文宣勁正","createTime":"2019-08-17T05:48:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T00:47:04.000Z","uid":187338,"like":145,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"0c82dee23bfb4b270f5b56c375c8280af6b84ffb","tid":1479914,"uid":187338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T05:48:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QHBwURx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQHBwURx.png&h=02c4142d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3wfmxDn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3wfmxDn.png&h=c7bd904c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cfDjjiE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcfDjjiE.png&h=a0ef3e4b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d2719ab914690146a0cde1d02c9091bf3af1d1bb","tid":1479914,"uid":274149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T06:16:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fce92f3e6c57091c1bfb7d520cbee4880703d1e","tid":1479914,"uid":227916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T12:45:20.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0987e3890674d84d323fb97493601e62a9b710d9","tid":1479914,"uid":23104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T12:47:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a18a966766fb32864a1f589e039bfe39abc7983","tid":1479914,"uid":59225,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T12:47:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">８１８安排</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1. 慢慢排入維園，入唔到就<span style=\"color: gold;\">坐低</span>，<span style=\"color: gold;\">直至集會結束為止</span><br />\n2. 集會結束後，不建議由天后或銅鑼灣走，<span style=\"color: red;\">去金鐘或中環走</span></span>"},{"pid":"e4324c722e8571288faf18f54d5e1fa728299bfd","tid":1479914,"uid":275243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T12:49:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"833ae529f28cd58a3b6a437e3426b96ff3bb0007","tid":1479914,"uid":129321,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:30:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AwA2mjW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAwA2mjW.jpg&h=27f8afe4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"647d34445cda5a69e9fab6320206cabe37fa21d9","tid":1479914,"uid":33875,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:33:23.000Z","msg":"馬鞍山勁多靚PEPE文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eb56d045694049c343c20d1fddf88d655ba6531","tid":1479914,"uid":268251,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:34:40.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個位.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FNrEn9y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFNrEn9y.jpg&h=3a63f7b3&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1481244/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1481244/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n原圖既少女, 係孤星淚入面既Cosette. 孤星淚係咩故事, 大家應該都知, 唔知自己google.<br />\n留意左好多文日, 我地既文宣其實可以利用唔同地方既文化,<br />\n加以更改, 達成更大效果. 要同全世界We Connect, 要活用唔同地方既文化.<br />\n孤星淚, 係歐美社會一定知道既title, 亦容易勾起佢地既共鳴.<br />\n大家不妨諗諗之後既文宣, 要更加creative.<br />\n<br />\n麻煩大家幫手forward去外國網站或者FB,<br />\n喺澳洲同法國既香港支持者受到大陸人攻擊之下,<br />\n呢張圖就係我地對外文宣既最佳利器.<br />\n當年南斯拉夫內戰, 打左幾年, 國際社會關注但唔出手,<br />\n最後係一張『薩拉熱窩的羅密歐與茱麗葉』既照片成為轉變關鍵.<br />\n羅密歐與茱麗葉既標題, 引起左歐美社會共鳴.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[文宣] 發夢之歌: 自由之旗・自由之民, 一首代表我地理念既歌.<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1476260/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1476260/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n我地唔單止要宣傳, 仲要有理念. 追求自由係最好既理念,<br />\n唔會嚇親老一派既香港人, 亦可以觸動到歐美社會既支持.<br />\n我選呢首歌既理由, 同上面講既『薩拉熱窩的羅密歐與茱麗葉』一樣,<br />\n都係能觸動歐美普世價值既issue. 對我地黎講, 一首好歌,<br />\n可以鼓舞士氣, 提醒我地不要放棄.<br />\n<br />\n上面條LINK係我搵既一首歌, 好適合我地用. 大家可以襟上去聽下首歌,<br />\n如果認同既話, 我希望可以搞個萬人齊唱版, 大家可以聽住音樂清唱,<br />\n唱完之後UPLOAD上上面條LINK, 我整合之後放出黎.<br />\n<br />\n文宣也好, 歌曲也好, 最重要係做得到be Symbol.<br />\nBatman曾有一段對話:<br />\n&ldquo;People need dramatic examples to shake them out of apathy,<br />\nand I can&rsquo;t do that as Bruce Wayne. As a man I&rsquo;m flesh and blood,<br />\nI can be ignored, I can be destroyed, but as a symbol,<br />\nas a symbol I can be incorruptible. I can be everlasting.&rdquo;<br />\n&mdash; Bruce Wayne (Batman Begins)<br />\n<br />\n我地既文宣同理念, 一定要做到be Symbol, 能有代表性, 見到某D文宣圖就諗起成個運動,<br />\n聽到某首歌就能夠代表我地並能觸動人心. 一切既品牌, 都係Symbol. 國旗係Symbol,<br />\n明星效應係Symbol. be Symbol, be Symbol, be Symbol. 重要事情講三次.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n818，維園見"},{"pid":"58b76c7fcb8a89f49ffc731610f61e1963b4cb6d","tid":1479914,"uid":104507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:35:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/call-official-recognition-chinese-communist-party-terrorist-organization \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fcall-official-recognition-chinese-communist-party-terrorist-organization%20&d=u3dPEc69Okhs1BcqxCk75WHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=806ddd73\" target=\"_blank\">http://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/call-official-recognition-chinese-communist-party-terrorist-organization </a><br />\n幫手廣傳出去阿！快d簽啦！<br />\n如果ccp係恐怖組織咁全世界先可以制裁佢咁先會幫到香港 美國佬都出緊力呀 快d配合把ccp定性為恐怖組織！<br />\n對準極權中共⚠️"},{"pid":"13345f23786e05f2fa5ab362f0cfadcde36d7021","tid":1479914,"uid":184374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:39:15.000Z","msg":"應該係暫時唯一無人拆嘅連儂牆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"856ed846f1af3741afb10d15e32da03a6c7165ee","tid":1479914,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"ci